videos.description: Josh Rosen pass complete to Austin Roberts for 49 yds to the ArzSt 21 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: J. Rosen pass to A. Roberts for 49 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: UCLA's Josh Rosen fumbles the ball giving up 5 yards, Arizona State's JoJo Wicker makes the recovery.
videos.headline: Rosen loses control of the ball

videos.description: Kalen Ballage run for a loss of 5 yards to the ArzSt 34 Kalen Ballage fumbled, recovered by UCLA Kenny Young
videos.headline: Botched handoff leads to Arizona State fumble

videos.description: Brady White pass intercepted Fabian Moreau return for no gain to the UCLA 33
videos.headline: B. White pass intercepted by F. Moreau

videos.description: QB Mike Fafaul connects with Nate Iese who pulls in a 25-yard pass with one hand.
videos.headline: UCLA's Iese casually pulls in one-handed catch

videos.description: UCLA quarterback Josh Rosen heads to the locker room with an apparent lower leg injury
videos.headline: Josh Rosen heads to locker room

videos.description: Mike Fafaul pass intercepted Gump Hayes return for 37 yds to the UCLA 4
videos.headline: Arizona State starts off second half with interception

videos.description: Demario Richard run for 5 yds for a TD
videos.headline: D. Richard run for 5 yds for a TD

videos.description: Josh Rosen pass complete to Soso Jamabo for 66 yds to the ArzSt 2 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: J. Rosen pass to S. Jamabo for 66 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Josh Rosen connects with Jordan Lasley who manages to stay on his feet and evade Arizona State defenders for a 52-yard touchdown. After the extra point, the Bruins tie the Sun Devils at 13 apiece.
videos.headline: UCLA's Lasley stays on his feet for 52-yard TD

videos.description: Arizona State's Brady White finds N'Keal Harry for a 14-yard touchdown to give the Sun Devils a 20-13 lead over UCLA.
videos.headline: Harry makes TD catch under pressure, Sun Devils take lead

videos.description: Josh Rosen pass intercepted Marcus Ball return for 22 yds to the UCLA 32
videos.headline: J. Rosen pass intercepted by M. Ball

videos.description: Arizona State kicker Zane Gonzalez now holds the NCAA record for field goals in a career. He made his 89th field goal Saturday in the Sun Devils' 23-20 win over UCLA.
videos.headline: ASU's Zane Gonzalez sets FBS record for career field goals made

videos.description: Josh Rosen pass complete to Nate Iese for 18 yds for a TD
videos.headline: J. Rosen pass to N. Iese for 18 yds for a TD

videos.description: Adarius Pickett picks off Arizona State's Dillon Sterling-Cole in the end zone in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: UCLA's Pickett makes wild INT in the end zone

videos.description: Mike Fafaul pass intercepted Robbie Robinson return for 3 yds to the UCLA 40
videos.headline: Interception seals win for Arizona State
